race.comment: Open race to close out the card. FAMILY OF LEAGUE (7) is a consistent conveyance hitting the top-five in seven of her past eight starts and is yet to miss a place in three starts over this distance range. Ready to peak third-up from the break and should be right there when the judge calls a halt. PIERONIMO (13) doesn't win out of turn but is usually thereabouts and should run his usual honest race despite the sticky draw. MY CHARM (12) broke the maiden status over this track and trip last time out and will have taken some confidence from that breakthrough victory. Stick with her. PERRI LASS (11) was a touch plain at the latest effort but the form prior was very consistent. In the mix if she brings her A-game. MR O'REILLY (2) best of the rest from the inside marble.
